flowchart TD
    Start([User calls RemoteMachine / Cluster / CloudManager])

    Start --> EntryChoice{Entry Point}

    %% ── Single-machine path (main flow) ──
    EntryChoice -->|"RemoteMachine(func, config, kwargs)"| RM_Run["RemoteMachine.run()"]

    RM_Run --> GenScripts["generate_scripts()
    ─────────────────
    • JobParams extracts func metadata
    • Renders Python wrapper from template
    • Renders shell launcher script
    • Embeds notification block
    • Saves configs to JSON"]

    GenScripts --> Submit["submit()"]
    Submit --> TransferMethod{config.transfer_method}

    TransferMethod -->|sftp| SFTP["transfer_sftp()
    SSH copies repo + data + scripts
    to remote machine"]
    TransferMethod -->|cloud| Cloud["transfer_cloud()
    Prepend rclone download
    commands to shell script"]

    SFTP --> Fire
    Cloud --> Fire

    Fire["fire()
    Execute shell script
    on remote machine via SSH"]

    Fire --> RemoteExec["Remote Execution
    ─────────────────
    1. secure_resources() — wait for lock
    2. Record start time
    3. Execute user function
    4. Record end time & status
    5. unlock_resources()
    6. Send email notification"]

    RemoteExec --> Monitor["check_job_status()
    Poll logs: queued → running → completed/failed"]

    Monitor --> StatusCheck{Status?}
    StatusCheck -->|completed| Download["download_results()
    SSH copy results back to local"]
    StatusCheck -->|failed| Failed([Job Failed])
    StatusCheck -->|running / queued| Monitor

    Download --> Done([Done])

    %% ── Multi-machine path (simplified) ──
    EntryChoice -->|"Cluster(func, hosts)"| ClusterFlow["Cluster.run()
    ─────────────────
    • Query each host's CPU/RAM
    • Split workload proportionally
    • Create RemoteMachine per host"]
    ClusterFlow --> RM_Run

    %% ── Cloud-managed path (simplified) ──
    EntryChoice -->|"CloudManager.serve()"| CMFlow["CloudManager
    ─────────────────
    • Lock-based job coordination
    • Periodic scheduler dequeues jobs
    • Monitors running jobs via rclone"]
    CMFlow --> RM_Run

    %% ── Styling ──
    classDef entryNode fill:#4a90d9,stroke:#2c5f8a,color:#fff
    classDef processNode fill:#f0f4f8,stroke:#7b8d9e,color:#1a1a1a
    classDef decisionNode fill:#ffeaa7,stroke:#d4a817,color:#1a1a1a
    classDef terminalNode fill:#55efc4,stroke:#00b894,color:#1a1a1a
    classDef failNode fill:#ff7675,stroke:#d63031,color:#fff

    class Start entryNode
    class RM_Run,GenScripts,Submit,SFTP,Cloud,Fire,RemoteExec,Monitor,ClusterFlow,CMFlow processNode
    class EntryChoice,TransferMethod,StatusCheck decisionNode
    class Done,Download terminalNode
    class Failed failNode
